#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.77"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.77:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.77:0.2"
msgid "8. Khajjanīyavagga "
msgstr "8. Itchy "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.77:0.3"
msgid "77. Dutiyaarahantasutta "
msgstr "77. The Perfected Ones (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.77:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.77:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.77:1.3"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.77:1.4"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; "
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.77:1.5"
msgid "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti … pe … evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.77:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi … saññāyapi … saṅkhāresupi … viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati. "
msgstr "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.77:2.2"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.77:2.3"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.77:2.4"
msgid "Yāvatā, bhikkhave, sattāvāsā, yāvatā bhavaggaṃ, ete aggā, ete seṭṭhā lokasmiṃ yadidaṃ arahanto”ti. "
msgstr "As far as there are abodes of sentient beings, even up until the pinnacle of existence, the perfected ones are the foremost and the best.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.77:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

